				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Gear Check level 63 bard<a name="41504"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">May 23 04 9:30 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Ally faction is required; if you are not so, there is the possibility you could get to ally from the next step down (warmly? brain fart) but it's not guaranteed.  Best to pick up giant warrior helms in the bazaar and turn them in.
<br />

<br />
Ears:  Replace the Dark Hoop.  Bloodmetal Earring of Engagement, Lupine Frenzy.  Aged Earring of Aptitude if people farm Droga on your server.
<br />
Neck:  Darkwater Pearl.
<br />
Face:  Painted Primal Mask, Face Mask of Frozen Mana
<br />
Head:  Dented Kunzar War Helm, Helm of Raldukan, Ice Forged Velium Helmet
<br />
Fingers:  good
<br />
Wrists:  Bracelet of Fortitude
<br />
Arms:  Feartouched Rubicite, Elbow Spiked, Dried Clay
<br />
Gloves:  Kylong Darkmail.  Personally I think ornate is wasted here.
<br />
Shoulders:  Draconic Pauldrons
<br />
Chest:  good
<br />
Back:  Personally, I love the Cloak of Greater Pernicity
<br />
Legs:  good
<br />
Waist:  aight, but look for a Soulscream belt, since you don't have haste
<br />
Boots:  Good, look for ornate
<br />
Weapons:  Look for instrument weapons, IE BDMG, Troubador's Mace, Etched Bone Spike, at least til you get Epic.
<br />
Range:  I like Idol of the Wavecrasher.
<br />
</span></td>
